#: details-widgets.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Value widget</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:126
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Use the calculator widget just like a normal calculator and once done "
#| "leave it by clicking on the '=' button or press the '=' key on your "
#| "keyboard."
msgid ""
"Use the calculator widget just like a normal calculator and once done leave "
"it by clicking on the <guibutton>=</guibutton> button or press the "
"<keycap>=</keycap> key on your keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Koristite grafičku kontrolu za digitron kao obični digitron i kada završite, "
"napustite je klikom na tipku '=' ili pritisnite tipku '=' na vašoj tastaturi."

#. Tag: title
#: details-widgets.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payee/Payer entry"
msgstr "Unos primatelja/pošiljatelja uplate"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The widget for entering a Payee/Payer is very similar to a typical combo-"
"box, but has some additional features."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-widgets.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Payee widget</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-widgets.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Payee widget</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:155
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you are requested to enter a payee/payer for a transaction, you can "
#| "start entering the name by pressing keys on your keyboard. As long as "
#| "matching entries exist in the list of payees/payers maintained by "
#| "&kappname; they will be presented in a box beneath or above the text "
#| "entry area. Using the mouse or the up/down keys one can select a name "
#| "from that list. Using the keyboard additionally requires you to select "
#| "the entry by pressing the RETURN key."
msgid ""
"When you are requested to enter a payee/payer for a transaction, you can "
"start entering the name by pressing keys on your keyboard. As long as there "
"are entries in the list of payees/payers maintained by &kmymoney; which "
"match the characters entered, they will be presented in a box beneath or "
"above the text entry area. Using the mouse or the &Up;/&Down; keys, one can "
"select a name from that list. Using the keyboard additionally requires you "
"to select the entry by pressing the &Enter; key. Clicking the X to the right "
"of the entry area clears the field. Clicking the down arrow to the right of "
"the X displays the complete list of possible payees/payers."
msgstr ""
"Kada se od vas zahtijeva da unesete primatelja/pošiljatelja uplate za "
"transakciju, možete početi unosom imena pritiskanjem tipki na vašoj "
"tastaturi. Sve dok postoje odgovarajući unosi u listama primatelja/"
"pošiljatelja uplata u vlasništvu &kappname;, bit će prikazani u okviru ispod "
"ili iznad oblasti za unos teksta. Korištenje miša ili tipki gore/dolje može "
"odabrati ime iz te liste. Korištenje tastature dodatno zahtijeva da unesete "
"ime pritiskom na tipku RETURN."

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:167
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If a name is entered that is not yet known to &kappname; you will be "
#| "asked if you want to create a new payee/payer record. If you do not wish "
#| "to do so, then the field will be blanked. Otherwise, the record will be "
#| "created and added to the list."
msgid ""
"If a name is entered that is not yet known to &kmymoney; you will be asked "
"if you want to create a new payee/payer record. If you do not wish to do so, "
"then the field will be blanked. Otherwise, the record will be created and "
"added to the list."
msgstr ""
"Ako je uneseno ime koje nije od ranije poznato &kappname; bit ćete upitani "
"želite li kreirati dosije za novog primatelja/pošiljatelja uplate. Ako to ne "
"želite, polje će biti prazno. U suprotnom , dosije će biti kreiran i dodan u "
"listu."

